---
import Layout from "../layouts/index.astro"

const ellip = ` … `
const md = " — "

const meta = {
	description:
		"At CyberFern, we guide startups to build strong, secure, and resilient foundations without breaking the bank. Our practical, straightforward approach helps you to understand and address your security needs, so you can focus on growing your business.",
	title: "Cyberfern.com | Free Startup Security Consultation",
}
---

<Layout {meta}>
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-text">
				<header>
					<h1>
						You grow your business{ellip}<br />We build your cyber-resilience
					</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Starting up is hard enough without worrying about cybersecurity.</p>
				<p>
					At CyberFern, we guide startups to build strong, secure, and resilient
					foundations without breaking the bank. Our practical, straightforward
					approach helps you to understand and address your security needs, so
					you can focus on <em>growing your business</em>.
				</p>
				<p class="lets-talk">
					<span>Let’s talk!</span>
					<a
						class="button"
						href="https://calendly.com/annalezhikova-ne7b/cybersecruitychat"
						rel="external"
						>FREE STARTUP SECURITY CONSULTATION</a
					>
				</p>
				<p>
					No pressure, no technical jargon{md}just straightforward guidance to
					help your startup grow securely
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-image">
				<img
					alt=""
					height="450"
					src="/images/ferns.jpg"
					width="675"
				/>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="what">
			<header>
				<h2>What We Do</h2>
			</header>
			<div class="card one">
				<img
					alt=""
					height="300"
					src="/images/risk-management.jpg"
					width="450"
				/>
				<h3>Assess your cyber risks</h3>
				<p>
					<strong>Know Where You Stand</strong>. We’ll review your current setup
					and identify what matters most for your startup’s security. Simple,
					practical, and focused on your actual risks.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card two">
				<img
					alt=""
					height="300"
					src="/images/assessments.jpg"
					width="450"
				/>
				<h3>Build a roadmap</h3>
				<p>
					<strong>Clear Steps Forward</strong>. Get a realistic plan that fits
					your budget and growth stage. We prioritise what’s crucial now and
					what can wait, so you can make informed decisions about your security
					investments.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card three">
				<img
					alt=""
					height="300"
					src="/images/training.jpg"
					width="450"
				/>
				<h3>Get help with implementation</h3>
				<p>
					<strong>Hands-On Support</strong>. Need help putting the plan into
					action? We’re here to guide you through each step, from setting up
					basic protections to training your team. No stress{md}just steady
					progress toward better security.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<div class="why">
			<heading>
				<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
			</heading>
			<p>
				Like the native ferns of New Zealand, we believe in supporting growth
				from the ground up. We’re passionate about <strong
					>helping startups lay down strong roots{md}with</strong
				> practical, budget-conscious security solutions focused on what matters
				most.
			</p>
			<p>
				What makes us different is our <strong>holistic vision</strong> of cybersecurity.
				We know that effective security isn’t just about technology{md}it’s
				about how your people work, how your processes flow, and how your
				business grows. By
				<strong>integrating</strong> all these elements, we create solutions that
				truly fit your startup’s reality and support your journey from day one.
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>
	<aside
		id="about"
		class="about"
	>
		<header>
			<h2>About CyberFern</h2>
		</header>
		<div class="about-content">
			<p>CyberFern was founded by Anna Lezhikova.</p>
			<p>
				She has more than twenty years of experience in communications, business
				management, software development, DevOps, and DevSecOps. She understands
				not only the technology, but also people and processes: the triad of
				good cybersecurity.
			</p>
			<p>
				Let&rsquo;s work together to protect what matters most to you and your
				organisation.
			</p>
		</div>
	</aside>
</Layout>
